sL.n: Colored text##Text can be colored just like an icon
Press me to echo 1, 2, 3 in order
Press me for a random echo
I am a subcategory##Hovering opens me, you can also press Ctrl + S too
I am an icon category##Using icons instead of text is easy! Just set the name to "::1" or some other number

sL.c: /echo An icon argument goes between "::" and the number to modify how the icon is displayed

sL.n: ::-1##This is where custom icon #1 would appear if you added one
sL.c: /echo Check the icon browser's "Custom" tab to learn how to add them

sL.n: ::66001##I can be any color you want
::90215##You can shift and rotate the image!
::68429##You can use these together to zoom in anywhere!
::152241##Most settings can be double or ctrl clicked to manually input values
::76613##Use spacers to align things or add some imagery
Open icon browser##You can also open this using the magnifying glass in the corner of shortcut configs
Category Behaviors##Changing the mode of a category will let them cycle through their internal shortcuts

sL.c: /echo These shortcuts also execute their commands!

sL.n: Animated Colors##You can animate colors by changing the color alpha to higher than 255
::60071##You must manually input these values by double or ctrl clicking the color alpha
Condition Sets##Enable and disable bars based on various states, set them up in the "Condition Sets" tab on the plugin config
Hotkeys##Execute a shortcut without clicking it, just like a hotbar. If a bar is disabled, its hotkeys are as well.
Exporting##Share bars and shortcuts by clicking the "Export" button when editing them
Importing##Import something by copying an export string and then clicking "Import" when creating a bar or shortcut
Backups##The config is automatically backed up when the plugin is updated, you can load them from the "Backups" tab on the plugin config
Debug Menu##Check internal information from the "Debug" tab on the plugin config, such as active hotkeys
Pies / Radial Menus##You can use a bar as a pie menu by adding a hotkey in its settings
Pie Restrictions##Pies will display up to 12 clickable shortcuts per ring, and up to 3 rings (2 categories deep)
Command /wait##Shortcuts cannot use macro specific commands such as "/wait", please run a macro instead with "//m"
Special characters ##You can right click on name / command inputs to insert special characters

/qolvisible off -DEMO-
